Admin Dashboard

{activeSection === "flights" && (

Add Flight

setNewFlight({ ...newFlight, flightNumber: e.target.value })} />
setNewFlight({ ...newFlight, destination: e.target.value })} />
setNewFlight({ ...newFlight, status: e.target.value })} />

Flights:

{flights.map((flight, index) => (
Flight {flight.flightNumber} to {flight.destination} - {flight.status}
))}
)} {activeSection === "passengers" && (

Add Passenger

setNewPassenger({ ...newPassenger, name: e.target.value })} />
setNewPassenger({ ...newPassenger, passengerNumber: e.target.value })} />
setNewPassenger({ ...newPassenger, flightId: e.target.value })} />

Passengers:

{passengers.map((passenger, index) => (
{passenger.name} - Passport {passenger.passengerNumber}
))}
)}
